{
  "text": "There have also been studies of the potential benefits of probiotics [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] , although they show varied performance against CDI in animals and humans [CITATION_3] . In addition, vaccines for humans are at various stages of development, although none is currently available for livestock.",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "15584033",
